description:
This week on Unqualified, Anna and Sim hang out with the wonderful Malin Akerman (Billions, Watchman, The Comeback)! Anna and Malin talk about being event buddies, female friendships, splitting the bill on the first date, and play "Finance Term or Sex Position?” Malin also braves some "Deal Breakers" and "How Would You Proceeds!”

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
